    <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingTwo">
        <div class="card-body">
            Users can notify and organize events on the fly with Notifly!<br /><br />
            Once registered, the admin can set up a gathering with one simple 
            text that sends out all the details to the whole group they've created. It's easy to respond to the invite too,  with a simple 
            'yes' or a 'no', with an identification number, it will automatically update their response in your personal table. The best part is, 
            you don’t need to open the application! Although the application is there to view all attendees, to alter any information in the groups, and more.  
            In about seconds, the user could get an organized activity up and ready.<br /><br/>
            It takes the hassle out of planning. Give Notifly!
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
